Fun Facts on India

Gujarat as a production base





Petrol Capital 
Denim City


Gujarat is an industrial powerhouse in West India, also known as the ‘Petrol Capital of India’ and an automobile manufacturing hub.select againmore
Gujarat, a textile industry manufacturing hub, is the third largest denim producer in the world.select againmore














